// Simple KaleshScript test

chutiye ye x hai 42
chutiye ye naam hai "Bhai"

bhauk "Hello from KaleshScript!"
bhauk naam
bhauk x

bsdk agar x > 40 kar:
    bhauk "X bada hai bc"
warna:
    bhauk "X chota hai"

chutiye ye count hai 0
jab tak maa count < 5 na maane:
    bhauk count
    count = count + 1

chutiye ye numbers hai [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
bhauk numbers[0]
bhauk numbers[2]

bhauk "Program khatam!"
